{"tid":2126720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧達智36小時未送院","createTime":"2020-07-27T04:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:19:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":137,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbcbda32f5ba749cf119d19f2c6553402fac0a0","tid":2126720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/XXLNR2X62T5HPINQLQIY3STC7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FXXLNR2X62T5HPINQLQIY3STC7A%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e8287d45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FXXLNR2X62T5HPINQLQIY3STC7A%2F&h=30d4f7d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/XXLNR2X62T5HPINQLQIY3STC7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鄧達智36小時未送院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2WyLvCUBp8j5GgJ3yY31rgXCGTM=/706x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VHOOWZ7JU7UGDX2WA7RA3DKZZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2WyLvCUBp8j5GgJ3yY31rgXCGTM%3D%2F706x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVHOOWZ7JU7UGDX2WA7RA3DKZZU.jpg&h=2de46a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】62歲的知名時裝設計師鄧達智本月24日初步確診，他按衞生署指引一直在元朗家中自我隔離，等署方派車送往醫院，但至昨日超過36小時仍未獲送院。本報記者昨致電詢問狀況，他表示：「前晚10點幾通知我等，𠵱家中午12點，已經超過36小時喇，仲未有消息話幾時安排，只可以繼續等住先。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n避見家傭未憂傳染<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭硬頸累事 建制也不滿<br />\n<br />\n鄧指身體狀況。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n藝人施匡翹早前確診，潛伏期曾到新城電台和無綫工作，新城知訊台執行總監程凱欣及一名營業部男員工相繼中招，鄧達智曾到新城、港台及三聯網台工作，「新城有好多錄音室，三聯嘅女PR後來又確診，我都唔知喺邊度傳染到」。"},{"pid":"7a6e0f3d92b65bf993a5453999119e1dc468524c","tid":2126720,"uid":14918,"like":135,"dislike":1,"score":134,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"警察入院洗唔洗等?"},{"pid":"3631966dc2b488c85db8e5ff49ff9bff9a7243dd","tid":2126720,"uid":54373,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"快d去鄧氏宗祠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46286f6858669f589557ba07ba41a779fdc49bf1","tid":2126720,"uid":127929,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似排急症咁排到自己好返先有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c09013c3c36bc91719faf561f637629149ef7","tid":2126720,"uid":25538,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"爆煲<br />\n處理唔到啦"},{"pid":"8d1d53f84472cad5fdbc450cc849de24aaab6b09","tid":2126720,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"777又一壯舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a31e8ee804e1744a425e26ebe2adc4fa2bce61f","tid":2126720,"uid":346806,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"如果我有野<br />\n我會去鯉魚門度假村門口訓算<br />\n唔想野比屋企人"},{"pid":"98ecac13909e4d8dd55fc51f3e131e8806e61b44","tid":2126720,"uid":30084,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"又話中左好大獲既? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358c403972aa2d26cf57b6a9d6638e61788c3065","tid":2126720,"uid":13663,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"就黎病好先入院 on9咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc5a561bf0bf4beccd8066e926cb8f0ca8d0792","tid":2126720,"uid":84116,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"名人都等咁耐<br />\n普通市民點算<img src=\"/assets